.TH "ISOTEST" "1" "May 4, 2022" "BlueZ" "Linux System Administration"
.SH NAME
isotest \- ISO testing
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
\fBisotest\fP <\fIMODE\fP> [\fIOPTIONS\fP] [\fIbdaddr\fP] [\fIbdaddr1\fP]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
\fBisotest(1)\fP is used to test Isochronous (CIS/BIS) communications on the
BlueZ stack
